-- Renamo-Loyal Militiamen Kill Three in Second Attack in Days
-- B y   W i l l i a m   F e l i m a o
-- 2013-04-06T20:48:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-06/renamo-loyal-militiamen-kill-three-in-second-attack-in-days.html
Three people died and at least five
were injured this afternoon in an attack attributed to
militiaman loyal to the main opposition party Renamo in the
central Mozambique province of Sofala.  Arnaldo Machavo, Chibabava district administrator, told TV
station STV in a telephone call the attack occurred around
5 p.m. local time.  It was the second attack in two days.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  